===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[know]]; to [[learn]]; to be [[inform]]ed of
#: {{zh-x|得悉|to know}}
#: {{zh-x|熟悉|to know clearly}}
# [[all]]; [[fully]]; [[entirely]]
